xwikidoc.content:
= Description =

This is a bridge macro between Confluence Note macro and XWikis Warning macro.

= Parameters =

|=Parameter|=Description
|**title**|The title of the note.

= Examples of usage =

== Example 1 ==

{{code}}
{{note title="Note: "}}
This is my note with title.
{{/note}}
{{/code}}

Result :

{{note title="Note: "}}
This is my note with title.
{{/note}}

== Example 2 ==

{{code}}
{{note title="It supports XWiki syntax: "}}
This is my note with title and a link [[XWiki Store>>https://store.xwiki.com]]
{{/note}}
{{/code}}

Result :

{{note title="It supports XWiki syntax: "}}
This is my note with title and a link [[XWiki Store>>https://store.xwiki.com]]
{{/note}}
